Package: handsontable
Type: Package
Title: Interface to the 'Handsontable' JavaScript Data Grid
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your Name", "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Handsoncode sp. z o.o.", role = "cph", comment = "Handsontable library")
    )
Description: Provides an R interface to the modern 'Handsontable' JavaScript library,
    a powerful data grid component that combines spreadsheet-like functionality with
    professional data grid features. Supports data validation, conditional formatting,
    formulas, sorting, filtering, and seamless integration with 'Shiny' applications.
